event DebugVerify(tuple(address from, address verifier, uint256 nonce) req, uint8 v, bytes32 r, bytes32 s, address signer)
event MetaTransactionExecuted(address indexed from, address indexed verifier, bool indexed verified)
event OwnershipTransferred(address indexed previousOwner, address indexed newOwner)
function _verify(tuple(address from, address verifier, uint256 nonce) req, uint8 v, bytes32 r, bytes32 s) view returns (bool)
function execute(tuple(address from, address verifier, uint256 nonce) req, uint256[8] proof, uint256 input, uint8 v, bytes32 r, bytes32 s) payable returns (bool)
function executeWithSignature(tuple(address from, address verifier, uint256 nonce) req, uint256[8] proof, uint256 input, bytes signature) payable returns (bool)
